parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's seat frame or bracket can cause the seat to become unstable or list to one side, potentially leading to accidents or injuries due to reduced driver control and comfort.
symptoms: The seat feels unstable or shaky
the seat is loose or broken on one side
the seat lists to one side
a loud pop or noise is heard when sitting in the seat.
